## UI Sections (Settings → Estimating Configuration)
1. **Difficulty Factors** - Site condition multipliers
2. **Height Adjustments** - Thresholds and multipliers
3. **Installation Types** - Surface/concealed/grouped factors
4. **Material Settings** - Waste allowances, volatility alerts
5. **Overhead & Profit** - Recovery percentages
6. **Taxes & Fees** - Sales tax, permits, standard charges
7. **Scheduling** - Productive hours, overtime rules

